{{醫學}}
'''醫學博士'''（{{lang-en|Doctorate of Medicine and of Philosophy}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：{{lang|en|MD–PhD}}）是{{le|醫師科學家|Physician-scientist}}的雙重學位，結合[[醫學士|醫學士]]學位（{{lang|en|MD}}）的職業培訓與[[哲學博士|哲學博士]]學位（{{lang|en|PhD}}）的研究專長；哲學博士學位在[[美國|美國]]及許多[[國家|國家]]是最高階[[學位|學位]]。[[國家衛生院_(美國)|美國國家衛生研究院]]補助50所[[醫學院|醫學院校]]的{{le|醫學科學家培訓計劃|Medical Scientist Training Program}}，以學費和津貼支持這些機構對醫學博士課程學生進行培訓，這些課程計畫相當競爭，有些課程每學年只招收兩個學生<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usnews.com/education/best-graduate-schools/top-medical-schools/articles/2014/02/27/merge-interests-in-science-medicine-with-an-md-phd|title=Merge Interests in Science, Medicine With an M.D.–Ph.D.|publisher=usnews.com|accessdate=2015-08-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906065240/http://www.usnews.com/education/best-graduate-schools/top-medical-schools/articles/2014/02/27/merge-interests-in-science-medicine-with-an-md-phd|archivedate=2015-09-06}}</ref>。醫學博士錄取者的[[MCAT|MCAT]]分數通常高於僅醫學士的錄取者<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.aamc.org/download/321548/data/factstableb10.pdf |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2018-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104073150/https://www.aamc.org/download/321548/data/factstableb10.pdf |archivedate=2018-01-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.aamc.org/download/321506/data/factstablea22.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-10-08 |archive-date=2018-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180420185855/https://www.aamc.org/download/321506/data/factstablea22.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 培訓計畫 ==
在[[美國|美國]]，可以經由某些醫學院提供的雙學位課程獲得醫學博士學位。綜合培訓計劃的想法始於1956年[[凱斯西儲大學|凱斯西儲大學]]{{le|凱斯西儲大學醫學院|Case Western Reserve University School of Medicine|醫學院}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mstp.cwru.edu/ |title=CWRU Medical Scientist Training Program (MSTP) |publisher=cwru.edu |accessdate=2012-06-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310193334/http://mstp.cwru.edu/ |archivedate=2012-03-10 }}</ref>，接著這個方法迅速傳到其他研究型醫學院。

== 事業途徑 ==
絕大多數（超過80%）的醫學博士畢業生最終會選擇進入{{le|學術機構|Academy}}、[[政府|政府]]、職責核心為醫學研究的[[企業|企業]]<ref name=Ley_2005>{{cite journal | author=Ley TJ| author2=Rosenberg LE | title=The physician-scientist career pipeline in 2005: build it, and they will come | journal=JAMA | date=2005 | pages=1343–51 | volume=294 | issue=11 | pmid=16174692 | doi=10.1001/jama.294.11.1343  }}</ref>。根據{{le|美國實驗生物學學會聯合會|Federation of American Societies for Experimental Biology}}在2000年進行的研究，由[[國家衛生院_(美國)|美國國家衛生研究院]]資助的{{le|醫學科學家培訓計劃|Medical Scientist Training Program}}畢業生每年僅佔[[醫學院|醫學院]]畢業生的2.5%，但畢業後約佔授予[[醫生|醫生]]的所有研究撥款的三分之一。許多醫學博士畢業生也在其專業領域臨床執業<ref name=Zemlo_2000>{{cite journal | author=Zemlo TR | author2=Garrison HH | author3=Partridge NC | author4=Ley TJ | title=The physician-scientist: career issues and challenges at the year 2000 | journal=FASEB J | date=2000 | pages=221–30 | volume=14 | issue=2 | pmid=10657979 | url=http://www.fasebj.org/cgi/content/full/14/2/221 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626000953/http://www.fasebj.org/cgi/content/full/14/2/221 | archivedate=2009-06-26 | doi=10.1096/fasebj.14.2.221 | access-date=2020-10-13 }}</ref>。

